## QA Publish Request

Include a machine-readable block in the PR body so the trusted GitHub Actions publish workflow can resolve issue metadata without shell access to Codex-local notes.

```json
{
  "issue_ref": "{{issue_ref}}",
  "run_dir": "artifacts/qa-runs/functional-qa/<target-slug>/<run-id>",
  "route": "/game",
  "scenario_seed": "",
  "checkpoint_id": "",
  "no_auto_evidence_upload": false
}
```

Maintainers can then trigger the trusted publish step with either:
- a PR comment: `/qa-publish`
- the `Trusted QA Publish` workflow with `pr_number`

